 using the same analysis techniques, we compare our\nresults with observations of the local Orion molecular clouds, placed at the\ndistance of M31 and simulated to appear as they would if observed by the SMA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jan 2020 10:36:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
