pot number is underestimated by about\n40\\%. The KO monthly averaged sunspot number data of both hemispheres is\nnormalized with the RGO monthly averaged total sunspot number data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jan 2020 12:13:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-10"}
