cal implications of discordant H0 values. Finally, I\nargue that now is a particularly opportune time to leverage the synergies\nbetween stellar physics and observational cosmology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jan 2020 14:43:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-10"}
